item.title: CVE-2019-4012|2024-08-04T19:26:27.666Z -- ibm -- bigfix%20webui%20profile%20management
item.description: IBM BigFix WebUI Profile Management 6 and Software Distribution 23 is vulnerable to SQL injection. A remote attacker could send specially-crafted SQL statements, which could allow the attacker to view, add, modify or delete information in the back-end database. IBM X-Force ID: 155886.
